      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Horror Adventures pg. 214</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> moderate necromancy <strong>CL</strong> 8th</p><p><strong>Price</strong> +2 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>This special ability functions as the <em>vampiric</em> special ability, except that the daily limit of healing from <em>greater vampiric</em> weapons is 5 hit points per Hit Die of the owner. A wielder can be attuned to only one <em>vampiric</em> or <em>greater vampiric</em> weapon at a time.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>cure moderate wounds</em>, <em>inflict moderate wounds</em>, <em>vampiric touch</em>; <strong>Price</strong> -</p>",
